{"tid":2041307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六國破滅 非兵不利 戰不善 弊在賂秦","createTime":"2020-05-29T07:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T07:45:46.000Z","uid":6030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"260d12423196418ec59eee7a1992e5129aa32d83","tid":2041307,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"六國的滅亡，不是（因為他們的）武器不鋒利，仗打得不好，弊端在于用土地來賄賂秦國。拿土地賄賂秦國虧損了自己的力量，（這就）是滅亡的原因。有人問：&ldquo;六國一個接一個的滅亡，難道全部是因為賄賂秦國嗎？&rdquo;（回答）說：&ldquo;不賄賂秦國的國家因為有賄賂秦國的國家而滅亡。原因是不賄賂秦國的國家失掉了強有力的外援，不能獨自保全。所以說：弊病在于賄賂秦國。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"8fcc2818ded87a5cdfb5ce4e910fcef574a8acae","tid":2041307,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"木鹿小王"},{"pid":"7e0b84a975a05d43263e87e8ed2bc7bf26544bf4","tid":2041307,"uid":231294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"今日割五城<br />\n明日割十城<br />\n香港人退無可退"},{"pid":"f43e4577273dd2fbf70fe0283d9cb15f9d8d8277","tid":2041307,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"你想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dea8af83e74dde99dd6de449655b605d2f9e66","tid":2041307,"uid":312193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"秦=支共？"},{"pid":"977a9a9286354c5287a0c2c3f0d96da6168a47f3","tid":2041307,"uid":37600,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"然後得一夕安寢"},{"pid":"d44215b2978912d8ec6e680cb54f426d1a425a31","tid":2041307,"uid":124180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2dea8af83e74dde99dd6de449655b605d2f9e66","tid":2041307,"uid":312193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"秦=支共？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"賂秦：德法伊朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj